1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,800
 You mean to say you copied someone else's consciousness without federal authorization?

2
00:00:03,800 --> 00:00:04,280
 Yes.

3
00:00:04,280 --> 00:00:08,480
 Suspect moving fast in sector B-54, all nearby units respond immediately.

4
00:00:08,480 --> 00:00:10,860
 My God, don't you know this is a federal felon?

5
00:00:10,860 --> 00:00:13,100
 So I found you, I just want to activate it.

6
00:00:13,100 --> 00:00:16,980
 The V-1 mind upload had flaws, I can't give it to you.

7
00:00:16,980 --> 00:00:18,680
 They're in the copy!

8
00:00:18,680 --> 00:00:21,160
 No more clothes!

9
00:00:28,540 --> 00:00:31,980
 An unregulated digital consciousness uploaded to the public network?

10
00:00:31,980 --> 00:00:33,500
 I can't bear the consequences.

11
00:00:33,500 --> 00:00:35,100
 Then why did you help build it?

12
00:00:35,100 --> 00:00:35,580
 Listen!

13
00:00:35,580 --> 00:00:38,540
 The Omega Life breach still haunts me.

14
00:00:38,540 --> 00:00:40,460
 That was a disaster, son.

15
00:00:40,460 --> 00:00:43,180
 You know what the rich do with your technology.

16
00:00:43,180 --> 00:00:49,420
 Listen, I'm just a scientist, I don't do politics.

17
00:00:49,420 --> 00:00:51,420
 All I know is this will tore society apart.

18
00:00:51,420 --> 00:00:52,700
 You better check this shit out.

19
00:00:52,700 --> 00:00:54,460
 Courts don't need testimony anymore.

20
00:00:54,460 --> 00:00:58,380
 Take the scrap if you want it.

21
00:00:58,540 --> 00:01:00,300
 Just scrub the serial numbers.

22
00:01:00,300 --> 00:01:03,980
 And just so you know, no one's ever put a mind in a machine before.

23
00:01:03,980 --> 00:01:05,580
 Think about the next generation.

24
00:01:05,580 --> 00:01:07,820
 It's already falling apart out there, Doctor.

25
00:01:07,820 --> 00:01:09,420
 I'm not doing this for you.

26
00:01:09,420 --> 00:01:11,020
 I'm doing it for them.

27
00:01:11,020 --> 00:01:13,020
 I'll ask you one last time.

28
00:01:13,020 --> 00:01:15,580
 Are you sure about this?

29
00:01:15,580 --> 00:01:25,580
 Hands up! You are arrested!

30
00:01:25,580 --> 00:01:26,620
 Hey!

31
00:01:28,540 --> 00:01:29,740
 I'm not going to die!

32
00:01:29,740 --> 00:01:30,380
 It burns!

